lyrics:
[Verse]
In the morning light, they gather as one
A peloton of dreamers, ready to run
Sprinters and grimpeurs, hearts fiercely aligned
Together they ride, in this epic grind

[Chorus]
Pedaling with passion, they push through the streets
United in their quest, as the rhythm beats
They ride for Tjeu Grasshopper, their fearless guide
To reach "The Little Oven," where dreams don't hide
